1
00:00:00,531 --> 00:00:05,055
♪A little bit sorry for my love for you♪

2
00:00:05,055 --> 00:00:10,559
♪Sorry, I was a little late♪

3
00:00:10,559 --> 00:00:16,987
♪I really want the unconscious longing
to appear faster♪

4
00:00:16,987 --> 00:00:21,467
♪Can I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once more♪

5
00:00:21,467 --> 00:00:25,915
♪Holding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journey♪

6
00:00:25,915 --> 00:00:30,826
♪The chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after another♪

7
00:00:30,826 --> 00:00:34,875
♪The promised moment
will definitely not be forgotten♪

8
00:00:34,875 --> 00:00:39,410
♪Can I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeat♪

9
00:00:39,410 --> 00:00:43,707
♪Start the countdown 4321,
a new scenery♪

10
00:00:43,707 --> 00:00:48,472
♪I want to see all the scenes about you♪

11
00:00:48,472 --> 00:00:51,963
♪No need to miss you anymore♪

12
00:00:51,963 --> 00:00:55,643
♪Right by your side♪

13
00:00:57,289 --> 00:01:00,667
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,667 --> 00:01:03,040
=Episode 3=

15
00:01:03,328 --> 00:01:10,528
(Four months ago)

16
00:01:14,080 --> 00:01:21,184
(WE Beauty Family)

17
00:01:25,666 --> 00:01:28,000
Look how poorly she dressed.

18
00:01:28,233 --> 00:01:31,233
Is she eligible
for the secretary of the president?

19
00:01:36,700 --> 00:01:38,500
Alright, next.

20
00:01:43,133 --> 00:01:43,933
Sit down.

21
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:49,866
Introduce yourself.

22
00:01:50,266 --> 00:01:51,200
Hello, everyone.

23
00:01:51,800 --> 00:01:53,666
My name is Jin Xi'en.

24
00:01:54,700 --> 00:01:56,700
I-I have a double degree

25
00:01:57,000 --> 00:02:02,100
in Business English
and Business Management.

26
00:02:03,266 --> 00:02:05,333
And I have published three papers.

27
00:02:06,466 --> 00:02:07,200
Please.

28
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:07,966
Take it away.

29
00:02:09,900 --> 00:02:11,233
What's that smell?

30
00:02:21,900 --> 00:02:23,933
You're hired, Jin Xi'en.

31
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,433
Miss Jin,

32
00:02:29,466 --> 00:02:31,733
I read your papers on Dawan Talent.

33
00:02:32,200 --> 00:02:33,533
I also published papers on it.

34
00:02:33,833 --> 00:02:35,000
I know how hard it is.

35
00:02:35,433 --> 00:02:38,000
Good. You're hired, Jin Xi'en.

36
00:02:48,900 --> 00:02:49,700
Stop.

37
00:02:59,500 --> 00:03:00,608
Do you remember me?

38
00:03:10,533 --> 00:03:11,500
I don't.

39
00:03:12,466 --> 00:03:14,100
I meet so many people every day.

40
00:03:17,500 --> 00:03:21,533
Miss Jin, it's time to get off work.
You may go and close the door.

41
00:03:23,766 --> 00:03:24,733
Miss Jin.

42
00:03:30,033 --> 00:03:32,533
I will make you remember me.

43
00:03:39,833 --> 00:03:43,700
Mom, Yuan, what's the matter?

44
00:03:44,133 --> 00:03:48,900
We need to hold a meeting
to talk about the Lihuai International.

45
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:37,408
You're the troublemaker, right?

46
00:04:46,133 --> 00:04:46,900
Come on.

47
00:04:46,900 --> 00:04:48,400
A woman? I don't hit women.

48
00:04:48,833 --> 00:04:50,433
Our Muay Thai gym isn't performing well.

49
00:04:50,666 --> 00:04:52,266
Let's just scare her.

50
00:04:52,500 --> 00:04:54,400
Just give her a warning.

51
00:04:55,300 --> 00:04:57,433
I despise men who hit women.

52
00:04:59,000 --> 00:04:59,800
Ahem.

53
00:05:00,500 --> 00:05:01,466
I warn you.

54
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:02,700
If you don't behave...

55
00:05:02,700 --> 00:05:04,100
Are you Ling Feng?

56
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:08,500
Looks like I'm famous.

57
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,466
Yes, it's me.

58
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:13,033
You can call me...

59
00:05:13,568 --> 00:05:14,144
Prince.

60
00:05:14,900 --> 00:05:15,700
Prince.

61
00:05:17,233 --> 00:05:19,400
Since you're my fan, I won't hit you.

62
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:22,133
But I have principles.

63
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:24,933
I hear that you're a bully at work.

64
00:05:25,266 --> 00:05:28,500
You use your power
to make your colleagues suffer.

65
00:05:29,500 --> 00:05:31,700
So I'm here to uphold justice...

66
00:05:33,766 --> 00:05:34,566
Go get her.

67
00:05:42,933 --> 00:05:44,900
I'll fight you then.

68
00:05:53,233 --> 00:05:56,800
I specialize in hitting men.
Every time I see you, I will hit you.

69
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,500
Feng, are you alright?

70
00:06:07,500 --> 00:06:09,733
She's my goddess.

71
00:06:11,233 --> 00:06:13,700
I hope to be hit every time I see her.

72
00:06:31,666 --> 00:06:34,466
Look, I'm flooded with messages
because of what you did.

73
00:06:39,966 --> 00:06:42,933
(Entering WE Group
has been my sister's dream)

74
00:06:42,933 --> 00:06:45,033
(and her life goal.)

75
00:06:45,033 --> 00:06:49,800
(As her sister,
I must help her pave a career path.)

76
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:55,000
(So I made a bold decision
to pretend to be her.)

77
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:59,000
(I'll let those
who have bullied my sister pay a price.)

78
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:01,200
She became a moron.

79
00:07:08,433 --> 00:07:11,400
Hello, I'm Jin Xi'en.
I'm coming back to work today.

80
00:07:13,491 --> 00:07:18,013
♪I pass through the crowd with you♪

81
00:07:21,043 --> 00:07:26,004
♪As if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each other♪

82
00:07:29,053 --> 00:07:34,877
♪When the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps in♪

83
00:07:34,877 --> 00:07:41,472
♪You come with light,
shining into my heart♪

84
00:07:41,984 --> 00:07:45,828
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

85
00:07:45,828 --> 00:07:49,949
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

86
00:07:49,949 --> 00:07:51,645
♪Open my secret♪

87
00:07:51,645 --> 00:07:57,693
♪I hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you♪

88
00:07:57,693 --> 00:08:01,565
♪Sinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper♪

89
00:08:01,565 --> 00:08:06,071
♪With each breath,
I can feel the sweetness♪

90
00:08:08,032 --> 00:08:14,781
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪
